text: Destiny Chukunyere (born 29 August 2002), known mononymously as Destiny, is a Maltese-Nigerian singer. She has competed in various competitions. She won the Junior Eurovision Song Contest 2015 representing Malta. She was a contestant on Britain's Got Talent 2017 and in 2020 she won The X Factor Malta. Destiny represented Malta at the Eurovision Song Contest 2021 with the song "Je me casse".
